<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Certificado Personal de Registro de Bicicleta</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 40px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .header h1 { font-size: 24px; margin: 0; }
    .header p { font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin: 5px 0; }
    .section { margin: 20px 0; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    .section h2 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; padding-bottom: 5px; margin: 10px 0; }
    .section p { margin: 5px 0; font-size: 11px; }
    .code-section { text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
    .short-code { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; font-family: monospace; }
    .full-code { font-size: 11px; font-family: monospace; margin-top: 10px; }
    .qr-code { display: inline-block; margin-left: 20px; vertical-align: middle; }
    .attestation { border: 1px solid #999; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 11px; }
    .signature-lines { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 11px; }
    .signature-lines div { margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 9px; color: #999; margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #999; padding-top: 10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>VeloPass</h1>
    <p>Certificado Personal de Registro de Bicicleta</p>
    <p>Doc #: {{bike.id}} | Emitido: {{generateDate}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="code-section">
    <span class="short-code">{{bike.shortRegNumber}}</span>
    <span class="qr-code">[Código QR]</span>
    <div class="full-code">Código Completo: {{bike.fullRegNumber}}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Información del Propietario</h2>
    <p><strong>Nombre:</strong> {{user.displayName}}</p>
    <p><strong>Nacionalidad:</strong> {{user.nationality}}</p>
    <p><strong>Residencia Legal:</strong> {{user.legalResidence}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Detalles de la Bicicleta</h2>
    <p><strong>Marca:</strong> {{bike.make}}</p>
    <p><strong>Modelo:</strong> {{bike.model}}</p>
    <p><strong>Año:</strong> {{bike.year}}</p>
    <p><strong>Tipo de Cuadro:</strong> {{bike.frameType}}</p>
    <p><strong>Color:</strong> {{bike.colour}}</p>
    <p><strong>Material:</strong> {{bike.frameMaterial}}</p>
    <p><strong>Número de Serie:</strong> {{#if bike.serialNumber}}{{bike.serialNumber}}{{else}}No proporcionado{{/if}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Registro BikeIndex</h2>
    {{#if bike.bikeIndexId}}
    <p><strong>ID:</strong> {{bike.bikeIndexId}}</p>
    <p><strong>Enlace:</strong> <a href="https://bikeindex.org/bikes/{{bike.bikeIndexId}}">https://bikeindex.org/bikes/{{bike.bikeIndexId}}</a></p>
    {{else}}
    <p>No registrado de forma cruzada</p>
    {{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="attestation">
    <p>Yo, {{user.displayName}}, confirmo que la información anterior es precisa según mi leal saber y entender.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="signature-lines">
    <div>Nombre (imprenta): _______________________________</div>
    <div>Firma: _______________________________</div>
    <div>Fecha: _______________________________</div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>VeloPass - https://github.com/VeloPass</p>
    <p>Generado: {{generatedAt}}</p>
    <p>Solo para uso personal</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
